desc: Ultra-cool, chic, & sleek streetwear for the modern world. A black owned company that does more than just make dope clothes. Our clothing is eco-friendly, casual wear, active wear, & leisure wear made in Chicago. Pass on our style to others with our clothing line & help support mental health initiatives & give back.

layout.text:
What Exactly Do We Do?
With Each Purchase we donate to people in need of clothes, shoes, hats and other resources like counseling, suicide prevention hotline and more.
With every purchase you ARE making a donation!
